### Changes in this version (8.0.0-pre.3) since 8.0.0-pre.2

#### New features:
 - [2026-05-19:]: added error reporting when trying to submit a method that does not exist
 - [2026-05-19:]: adjusted API for jobs to better include relationships
 - [2026-05-08:]: added support for submitting matrices with IDs & overrides
 - [2026-05-08:]: added initial support for supplying overrides for library methods
 - [2026-04-28:]: switched header in emails to inverted design
 - [2026-04-28:]: added domain to email CID
 - [2026-04-28:]: added HTML email template
 - [2026-04-27:]: added initial implementation of server mail
 - [2026-04-29:]: jwt signing can now use either RSA or ECDSA keys
 - [2026-04-29:]: increased duration on machine files to reduce check-out frequency
 - [2026-04-29:]: added network:timeout config option and implemented timeout for requests
 - [2026-04-27:]: added support for RI-J as well as RI-JK
 - [2026-02-19:]: added initial support for PySCF density fitting (SCF only for now)
 - [2026-04-24:]: added billing
 - [2026-04-22:]: servers now check cert age before refreshing
 - [2026-04-22:]: added more authentication levels to server endpoints
 - [2026-04-22:]: switched JWT key auth to using server certs
 - [2026-04-22:]: servers now check cert age before refreshing
 - [2026-04-21:]: digichemd executable now includes server by default
 - [2026-04-20:]: added digichemd startup script
 - [2026-04-20:]: updated service script
 - [2026-04-20:]: added service file for running with systemd
 - [2026-04-20:]: server objects now write their PID to a plaintext PID file
 - [2026-04-17:]: removed debugging
 - [2026-04-17:]: added temp debugging to slurm calls
 - [2026-04-15:]: added get_billing endpoint
 - [2026-04-15:]: added supports_billing property to destinations
 - [2026-04-14:]: SLURM account data is now returned in a proper hierarchy
 - [2026-04-14:]: added more descriptive error message for missing db
 - [2026-04-14:]: added initial endpoint for fetching billing
 - [2026-04-14:]: added get_billing_account() and get_billing() methods to SLURM
 - [2026-04-13:]: added BILLING status
 - [2026-04-13:]: added get_share_data() method
 - [2026-04-13:]: added support for using the submitting user's ID as the billing account
 - [2026-04-13:]: added support for sshare command
 - [2026-04-11:]: added better error message for when no local user credentials are available
 - [2026-04-11:]: added db_name property to database for better error reporting
 - [2026-04-10:]: added initial billing support to SLURM
 - [2026-04-10:]: added get_local_user() function
 - [2026-04-10:]: added user set and user info programs
 - [2026-04-10:]: added ability to specify login duration
 - [2026-04-10:]: added local user login functions
 - [2026-04-09:]: added abiltiy for server to listen on all hosts, added port to server config, and allowed 0 for keep_alive
 - [2026-04-08:]: greatly expanded firestore support
 - [2026-04-08:]: added better debug info when submitting info to DB after job completion
 - [2026-04-02:]: added better error reporting when parsing a malformed method
 - [2026-04-02:]: improved error messages in server locking
 - [2026-04-02:]: directory endpoint now uses user run dir
 - [2026-04-02:]: added option to disable combined reports
 - [2026-04-02:]: multi-user servers now use separate run dirs for each user
 - [2026-04-02:]: added safe_access to some server endpoints
 - [2026-03-23:]: switched firestore to use bulk_writer()
 - [2026-03-21:]: added better interfaces for fetching results from mongita and firestore DBs
 - [2026-03-21:]: removed unsupported unqlite
 - [2026-03-20:]: added initial user permission protection to job DB
 - [2026-03-20:]: added initial support for userIds in job and result database
 - [2026-03-20:]: added users/self endpoint
 - [2026-03-20:]: added /users/self end point to test user mechanism
 - [2026-03-20:]: Server now issues a warning if there is no authentication enabled at all
 - [2026-03-20:]: added authentication to all endpoints
 - [2026-03-20:]: added better error logging for user auth and added config option to enable or disable user auth
 - [2026-03-19:]: added initial ability to authorise users
 - [2026-03-18:]: finished adding support for firebase for main functions
 - [2026-03-18:]: started adding support for status keywords
 - [2026-03-18:]: added Status_keywords type
 - [2026-02-18:]: The digichem version is now printed to the main log file

